Compilation* ( future plan )

1. OVERVIEW:
This is not an in-depth course; it is designed for users who want a collection of videos on a specific topic. There is no structured course or step-by-step approach, just a compilation of similar videos.
EXAMPLES ;

CASE 1:
The user wants podcasts featuring Elon Musk. The app will search YouTube and gather all of Elon Musk’s podcasts.
This is an easy one, not a big difference from YouTube.

CASE 2:

In this example, the user wants to gather all of Elon Musk’s talks specifically about Tesla and its future. The AI will sift through a variety of sources, including podcasts, interviews, videos, news articles, research papers, and documents. From this extensive pool of content, the AI will filter out only the relevant material focused on “Tesla and its future.”

After the filtration process, the user will receive only the pertinent videos. Additionally, the specific timestamps will be provided to indicate exactly where in each video Elon discusses Tesla.

This approach saves the user time by eliminating the need to browse through unrelated videos and content, allowing them to concentrate solely on information about “Tesla and its future.”

