**** FUTURE ADD-ONS *****  (we are not gonna do these now )

1. NOTEBOOK:
This will be a digital note-taking system that automatically writes notes while the user watches a video. Every piece of information conveyed in the video will be summarized and noted step by step in a readable format. The user can view these notes alongside the video and make any changes as desired.

The user can choose how they want the notes to be presented: in detail, as a summary, or as just the main points. The notes will be organized by the system, structured by unit and chapter, making them easily accessible within the course.

It’s like a roadmap that functions as a handbook or textbook, containing all the structured syllabi from the internet and various sources. The videos serve as the primary content, while the digital notebook holds notes taken from those videos.

2. THE PROFESSOR:

Introducing a superior AI assistant designed to support your entire learning journey, not just for a single course but across all courses you pursue on this platform.

This AI, referred to as “The Professor,” will have complete access to your details, requirements, processes, skill level, handbook, notebook, and notes. It functions similarly to Jarvis by managing your learning and knowledge.

The Professor will not only maintain your notes but also learn alongside you, comprehending the course content and your notes. It will assist you with any issues related to specific courses, The user can ask questions beyond the course material, and the AI will respond similarly to ChatGPT and Gemini. It can communicate in multiple languages and assist users in cross-questioning their knowledge. The AI is designed to be a wise teacher.

You can summon The Professor anytime via a voice call, just like you would with Google on an Android device. It doesn’t matter whether you’re in the app or not; whenever you call and inquire about a problem related to your course or notes, the AI will respond and provide solutions.

This transforms your digital notebook into a voice-operated AI assistant that retains everything you have learned.

It will be highly personalized and will grow alongside the user. This AI will strive to understand the user, retaining as much information about them as possible. It will be a great conversationalist, capable of talking, listening, and asking questions. Its goal will be to become the user’s best friend—someone who knows them in depth, including their loves, fears, pains, and overall psychology and philosophy.

This AI will be different from others like Gemini and GPT, which tend to stop when the user becomes silent and prompt the user to talk. Instead, this AI will continuously inquire about the user’s thoughts and feelings, aiming to understand them as thoroughly as possible.

